<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.9">
<l>kāmaṉkaṇaik kōrilakkamāy nalattiṉmiku</l>
<l>pūmarukō lanampeṇmaicin tittirātupōy</l>
<l>tūmalarnīr koṭutōḻinām toḻutēttiṉāl</l>
<l>kārmukilvaṇṇa raikkaṇkaḷāl kāṇalāṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without staying, becoming a target for Kāma’s arrows,</l>
<l>Fretting about our femininity, its nature greatly beautified  by virtue,</l>
<l>Leaving [here], friend, if we adore and praise [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">with pure blossoms and water,</l>
<l>Might we see the raincloud-hued one with [our own] eyes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
